{
  "title": "上海市奉贤区人民政府印发《关于全力打造国家级中小企业科技创新活力区的若干意见》的通知",
  "createTime": "2022年8月19日",
  "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: center; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 21pt;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">沪奉府发〔</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2022〕7号</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">各镇人民政府，街道办事处，开发区管委会，区政府各部门：</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">现将《关于全力打造国家级中小企业科技创新活力区的若干意见》印发给你们，请认真按照执行。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 27pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h5 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin-left: 0pt; line-height: 27pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></h5>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: right; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2022年8月19日&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（此件公开发布）</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: center; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">关于全力打造国家级中小企业科技创新</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: center; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">活力区的若干意见</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">为全面贯彻落实党的十九大和十九届历次全会精神和区五次党代会精神，紧紧围绕国家级中小企业科创活力区建设，坚持创新驱动、转型升级，发挥科学技术是第一生产力、人才是第一资源、创新是第一动力、金融是第一资本的作用，充分释放企业创新活力，营造中小企业蓬勃发展的创新生态，不断提升区域创新效能，为回答好新时代</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;奉贤美、奉贤强&rdquo;的新答卷做出科技创新工作积极贡献。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">一、主要目标</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">按照上海建设具有全球影响力的科创中心目标，全力打造国家级中小企业科技创新活力建设。力争到</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2025年，奋力实现&ldquo;三个翻一番&rdquo;，即：高新技术企业认定数量翻一番，达到2700家；每万人口高价值发明专利拥有量翻一番，达到20件；科技创新创业载体数量翻一番，达到24家；努力实施&ldquo;四个创新行动计划&rdquo;，即：小巨人企业认定数达到600家以上；企业技术（研究）中心达到400家以上；院士专家工作站达到100家以上；科技企业上市数量达到40家以上。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">二、具体举措</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（一）优化科技创新功能布局，打造协同发展创新空间</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">把握自贸区新片区重大机遇，积极主动融入长三角一体化战略、虹桥国际开放枢纽，按照产业集聚、创新融合、功能聚合的原则，加快形成分工明确、布局合理、协同发展的创新空间区位布局。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.加快打造东方美谷科技创新核心功能区。着眼于打造美丽健康产业创新策源地，进一步强化资本集聚、技术集聚、人才集聚，使之成为全区创新驱动的引领区、转型发展的示范区。加大力度引进、集聚创新企业和研发机构，发挥东方美谷产业研究院等功能型平台作用，支持技术研发和转化应用，形成国内乃至亚洲规模顶级、具有自主创新能力和核心竞争力的美丽健康特色产业集群。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">2.打造&ldquo;未来空间&rdquo;智能制造产业集群高地。抢抓新能源汽车风口，聚焦智能网联汽车全产业链，建设一批车路协同新应用场景，重点推进自动驾驶汽车测试示范区、智能网联信息安全平台、智能网联新能源汽车技术创新平台等建设，打造聪明路、未来车、智慧城，努力让未来空间成为上海汽车产业&ldquo;第三极&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">3.做大做强&ldquo;数字江海&rdquo;产业集群。抓住城市数字化转型的重要战略机遇和元宇宙等新兴产业发展机遇，以&ldquo;城市力全渗透的数字化国际产业社区&rdquo;为定位，用数字化方式打造未来城市，加快推进数字产业化、产业数字化。建设高标准的信息基础设施和数字底座，推动研发、制造、展示、营销等产业功能和商业、居住、服务、公共活动等城市功能的高水平融合，实现产城融合发展。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（二）强化企业创新主体地位，提升自主创新能力</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">坚持</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;移大树、育小苗，抢赛道&rdquo;，构建以&ldquo;科技型中小企业-高新技术企业-科技小巨人企业-科技企业上市&rdquo;为重点的企业梯度培育体系，激发市场主体创新活力，弘扬企业家精神，推动科创企业上新赛道、中小企业上规模、优质企业上市。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.加强引进龙头企业。瞄准世界500强、行业50强龙头企业，积极引进跨国公司研发中心，鼓励跨国公司设立分支机构和研发平台，发挥龙头企业引领、辐射和带动作用。加快传统产业链优化升级，推动传统产业通过全产业链整合升级向专业化和价值链高端延伸。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">5.培育具有高发展潜力的科技型企业。聚焦&ldquo;五型经济&rdquo;，实施&ldquo;淘金工程&rdquo;，以&ldquo;科技小巨人&rdquo;培养计划为突破口，通过精准排摸、多维筛选，助推企业加速发展。实施&ldquo;高新技术企业倍增计划&rdquo;，注重对初创期、成长期科技创新潜力企业的培育。制定&ldquo;科技小巨人、专精特新小巨人培育计划&rdquo;，围绕我区战略新兴产业，培育发展潜力大、创新能力强、市场竞争优势突出的企业，努力造就一批产业细分领域的&ldquo;隐形冠军&rdquo;，发挥标杆引领作用。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">6.助力推进科技企业上市。筛选区内潜在优质科创企业，建立区科技企业拟上市企业后备库，鼓励和引导区内科技企业做大做强。积极帮助企业疏通上市堵点，并在发展用地保障、申报科技和产业化项目等方面，对后备上市企业给予相应支持。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（三）加强产教融合发展，打造高水平功能型平台</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">大力建设高水平、新模式的科技创新功能型平台和创新创业载体，拓展提升平台载体的创新能级和服务能力，充分发挥其对创新创业的助推和支撑作用。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">7.打造高水平产学研协同创新平台。深入推进南部三区两镇联动发展，湾区建设提档升级，融合&ldquo;一流高校、高端产业、生态旅游、创新策源&rdquo;等要素资源，深化区校融合，加强大学科技园建设，推动科技成果加速转化。充分利用大学及科研院所科技研发资源，探索共建技术中心及海内外研发中心，打造国际科技创新交流平台，不断提升奉贤科技创新的浓度。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8.促进新型研发机构和功能型平台建设。对标国际最高水平，不断拓展提升平台载体的创新能级和服务能力。积极推进市级重点实验室、技术创新中心等科研基地在奉贤布局落地，支持建设企业技术中心及工程技术研究中心。加强院士专家工作站建设，充分利用院士专家智力资源，提供战略咨询、科技攻关等服务。支持民营企业牵头和参与建设市级科技创新基地。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">9.加强孵化器等创新创业载体建设。加强培育和引进企业孵化器、众创空间等创业载体，加大扶持力度，创新管理机制，提高孵化器建设水平，吸引优质科技企业拎包入住。建成集政策培训、人才教育、技术交易等为一体的综合体大楼，形成特色众创生态集聚区。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（四）优化创新要素配置效率，建设创新资源融合高地</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">强化科技创新公共投入的导向作用，充分发挥市场配置创新资源的作用，探索建立科创政策超市，以</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;揭榜挂帅&rdquo;激发创新活力，建成科技创新要素集聚、配置优化、效率突出的创新枢纽。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">10.优化财政资金扶持方式。进一步加大财政科技扶持力度，强化前置引导和后置激励相结合原则，支持本区各类创新创业主体。设立&ldquo;奉贤区支持创新创业发展专项资金&rdquo;，发挥科创投资基金作用，吸引更多社会资本加入，整合条线扶持资金，强化统筹管理，聚焦重点产业，增加政策的精准性和穿透力。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">11.创新科技金融服务支撑。探索建立&ldquo;基地+基金&rdquo;模式，推动科技与金融的高质量集聚。加强金融服务平台建设，创新融资方式，打造拨、投、贷联动的科技金融生态服务体系，引导创投资基金投资本区科技企业，引导金融机构为中小科技企业提供金融产品和服务。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">12.加大知识产权的运用和保护。整合知识产权管理部门、金融机构、交易机构、服务机构、园区及其企业的力量，引入高素质服务机构，用好各方资源，促进知识产权交易，开展专利预警、评议和导航，激发我区知识产权总体运营水平，为企业提供创新指引。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（五）强化科技人才队伍建设，建设创新人才汇聚高地</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不拘一格招才引智，加快&ldquo;滨海贤人&rdquo;集聚。实施更加开放、包容的人才体制机制，使各类人才的创新创业创造活力得以充分发挥，建成科技创新人才广泛汇聚、有序流动、创新活跃的人才高地。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;13.加大优秀科技人才引进和支持力度。依托海外高层次青年人才工程、科技部创新人才推进计划等国家重大人才计划，重点引进奉贤创新发展中紧缺急需的科技领军人才、优秀科技创新团队和高潜力青年人才。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">14.优化科技人才流动和激励机制。发挥市场配置科技人才资源的基础作用，充分调动用人主体积极性，支持、鼓励用人单位加大科技创新人才投入。进一步完善新型研发机构灵活用人的机制设计，探索&ldquo;双聘&rdquo;人员身份管理和人才共享机制创新。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">15.完善优化创新创业生态。实施&ldquo;四叶草&rdquo;工程，打造人力资源集聚、公共服务配套、生态人文转化、优质物业供给四大平台。以企业集聚度、活跃度、感受度作为衡量标准，变&ldquo;保姆式服务&rdquo;为&ldquo;妈妈式服务&rdquo;。用产业链集聚人，用活动吸引人，实施人才&ldquo;百千万&rdquo;工程，打造国际化人才高地。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 28pt; background: #ffffff;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>"
}